00:11:37.640 --> 00:11:40.860 align:middle line:84%
>> When you talk about fear,
you said there were two steps.

00:11:40.860 --> 00:11:43.740 align:middle line:84%
And the first one was
facing the inevitable.

00:11:43.740 --> 00:11:44.540 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, it was--

00:11:44.540 --> 00:11:45.280 align:middle line:90%
>> Can I handle it?

00:11:45.280 --> 00:11:45.500 align:middle line:90%
