00:11:47.667 --> 00:11:49.700 align:middle line:10%
Because a lot of times,
fear is magnified to us.

00:11:49.700 --> 00:11:52.790 align:middle line:84%
So we have to balance that
against the opportunity

00:11:52.790 --> 00:11:56.300 align:middle line:84%
and the likelihood of
what mixture of that fear

00:11:56.300 --> 00:11:59.202 align:middle line:84%
